        "TileImage": "$($repository e5cd7d51-fa8f-42fb-93de-c885b45a0925).Image",
        "Description": "Hanna Olsen is a prodigy doctor who always dreamed of working at an elite hospital like Gama. Two months into her engagement with world renown motorcyclist Joey Avery, her wish came true. There was only one catch, if she wanted the job she needed to find a last minute organ donor for a VIP patient. \rJoey fit the bill. She betrayed her love and allowed Gama to turn him into an unwilling organ donor.\rThe Avery family have found the truth. Now they want justice for their son. Good luck 47.",
